Catherine Frot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catherine_Frot 0 Catherine Frot ([kaˈtʁin_ˈfʁo]; born 1 May 1956) is a French actress. A ten-time César Award nominee, she won the awards for Best Actress for Marguerite (2015) and Best Supporting Actress for Family Resemblances (1996). Her other films include Le Dîner de Cons (1998), La Dilettante (1999) and Haute Cuisine (2012). Catherine_Frot ( [_kaˈtʁin __ˈfʁo_] ; born_1_May_1956 ) is a_French_actress .
